  "body": "### Description\nAs a staker, I may want an option that maximizes my hardware value, but doesn't allow me to serve full sets of data to my peers. I cannot serve old blocks when requested, but may have a smaller disk for home staking. \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\nThe profile implements the following defaults\n- Sync mode: CHECKPOINT\n- Data-storage-format: BONSAI\n    - bonsai-historical-block-limit: 128\n- Max-peers: 25 \n- -Xp2p-peer-lower-bound=10\n\n- Chain-pruning: Enabled\n    - Deposit logs / tree dependency (TEKU ONLY --> Consider later for BeKu ) ",
